    <section name="Expression step">

      <p>This step allow to compute expression for the alignment of unique mapped reads.</p>  

      <ul>
         <li><b>Name</b>: expression.</li>
         <li><b>Available</b>: Both local and distributed mode.</li>
        <li><b>Input</b>: filtered alignments</li>
        <li><b>Output</b>: expression file</li>
	 <br/>
         <li><b>Optional parameters</b>: none</li>
	<!--table>
		<tr><th>Parameter</th><th>Value</th><th>Description</th></tr>
		<tr><td>tmpdir</td><td>directory path</td><td>Directory for sort temporary file. Only in local mode.</td></tr>
	</table-->
       </ul>
      
	<p>In local mode, use the <b>main.tmp.dir</b> global parameter to set the temporary directory if this step fails with a full disk error.</p>

    </section>


